    <section class="section section-gray">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="coverage-grid">
                <div class="coverage-content">
                    <p class="section-label">Our Location</p>
                    <h2>Based in <span class="gradient-text">Rochester, NY</span></h2>
                    <p>
                        Our office is based in Rochester, NY, with our warehouse centrally located in Ontario, NY, giving us easy access to businesses throughout Western and Central New York including Rochester, Buffalo, Syracuse, and surrounding areas.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Don't see your city listed? Contact us anyway - we're happy to discuss projects outside our typical service area for larger installations.
                    </p>
                    <div style="margin-top: 24px;">
                        <strong style="color: var(--dark-gray);">Office:</strong><br>
                        <span style="color: var(--gray-600);">2480 Browncroft Blvd, Suite 206<br>Rochester, NY 14625</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
